name: freexl
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "1.0.2" %}

package:
    name: freexl
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: freexl-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: http://www.gaia-gis.it/gaia-sins/freexl-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    md5: 9954640e5fed76a5d9deb9b02b0169a0
    patches:
        - makefile.vc.patch  # [win]
        - nmake.opt.patch  # [win]
        - freexl.c.patch  # [win]

build:
    number: 1
    features:
        - vc9  # [win and py27]
        - vc10  # [win and py34]
        - vc14  # [win and py35]  

requirements:
    build:
        - python  # [win]
        - libiconv
        
    run:
        - libiconv
        
test:
    commands:
        - test -f ${PREFIX}/lib/libfreexl.a  # [unix]
        - conda inspect linkages -n _test freexl  # [linux]

about:
    home: https://www.gaia-gis.it/fossil/freexl/index
    license: LGPL-2.1
    summary: Extract valid data from within an Excel

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
